{"tid":1701084,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返緊五日半，好想辭","createTime":"2019-11-08T23:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:39:51.000Z","uid":56707,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6afb27f1ed8789429a5d85563488b9cba89704","tid":1701084,"uid":56707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:52:10.000Z","msg":"日日都好撚攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然啲同事係幾好，但嗰種攰真係從來未試過，不過年尾係咪搵到伏工嘅機會好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fecaf0c5da9e3f5ab4c9d609be72df2391d424","tid":1701084,"uid":212623,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T23:52:58.000Z","msg":"辭"},{"pid":"f095ae4e95d1d07541f8f09e9fafa4fde9bb3879","tid":1701084,"uid":152371,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:48:12.000Z","msg":"過5日半真係好辛苦"},{"pid":"08caf30c88bb445d711b2c0ef7d579b398af7be9","tid":1701084,"uid":226829,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"真心覺得5日半，一星期得一晚可以無憂咁去夜街同夜訓，再只得一日可以晏起既生活，真係好痛苦，同埋去個銀行郵局都好困難，呢D日子都唔知點過(唔好同我拗咁做銀行郵局D人又點，呢類行業唔返shift開夜晚同星期六日全日，只開office hour，本身已經係好有問題)<br />\n<br />\n6日更加唔使講"},{"pid":"53086362059b1be3c074d347b34ef1029f1e8beb","tid":1701084,"uid":86623,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"除非你已經搵到工/本身冇乜負擔, 否則絕對唔建議你呢個時候辭<br />\n<br />\n我八月裸辭, 每個星期都keep住有in有send cv, 前日先見得成<br />\n<br />\n雖然你睇恆生指數, 由緊急法[5/10]到今日仲升咗千幾點on99咁, 但出面個市就唔係咁, 好多公司請人都審慎好多"},{"pid":"720f42dd339bb3f1e4e77b8319cd5b8be0f98cac","tid":1701084,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"我以為自己出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有同老細傾 5日"},{"pid":"fe6e6576bd8ef05f9b460c85d1207263d2641662","tid":1701084,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"後生仔咁唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我返7日都未出聲<br />\n又養得起頭家"},{"pid":"7552d4292fe2f30960a80a391437033d0150761e","tid":1701084,"uid":248644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"工程？"},{"pid":"3ee1116829b264facb273a0cf60e30d7daa45bc6","tid":1701084,"uid":334593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:03:06.000Z","msg":"5日半真心屌唔住，我就唔會搵<br />\n利申:搵咗2個星期工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時有offer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8895f769e659c592dda4558add9f65557eb41421","tid":1701084,"uid":56707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720f42dd339bb3f1e4e77b8319cd5b8be0f98cac","tid":1701084,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"我以為自己出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有同老細傾 5日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:20.000Z","msg":"老細係鬼佬，覺得冇問題，話咁可以慳人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d22ee741859e16efb92b6ed6262900fe04bbfe","tid":1701084,"uid":209306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8895f769e659c592dda4558add9f65557eb41421","tid":1701084,"uid":56707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720f42dd339bb3f1e4e77b8319cd5b8be0f98cac","tid":1701084,"uid":163791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"我以為自己出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有同老細傾 5日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:20:20.000Z","msg":"老細係鬼佬，覺得冇問題，話咁可以慳人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T00:35:12.000Z","msg":"同你減返1日嘅人工<img src=\"/asset